message: Good day Bob, I'm pleased to offer you our premium product. Given its exceptional value, I'm sure you'll find our price of $1600000 quite reasonable.

Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the value of your premium product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $900000. I believe this is a fair price considering the market and my budget.

Hi Bob, after careful consideration, I'm willing to lower our price to $1400000. This reflects a significant reduction from our initial offer and demonstrates our commitment to reaching an agreement with you.

Hi Alice, I appreciate the reduction in price, but I still think we can find a better middle ground. I'm willing to increase my previous offer to $1050000, which I believe is a fair compromise considering both our interests.
